    {
      "id": "b1a06195-285f-46c2-9cea-2fbcfbb9dc14",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$u_n^2=(2^{n+1}+1)^2=2^{2n+2}+2^{n+2}+1=10...010...01_2$ ($n-1$ puis $n+1$ chiffres $0$)",
        "html": "<p><span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(u_n^2=(2^{n+1}+1)^2=2^{2n+2}+2^{n+2}+1=10...010...01_2\\)</span>\n(<span class=\"math inline\">\\(n-1\\)</span> puis <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(n+1\\)</span> chiffres <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(0\\)</span>)</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a067a466-b382-4e20-9a12-c49c93ef2387",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$u_n^3$,",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(u_n^3\\)</span>,</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2c4a1171-6aee-4e8c-ba3b-797ca6f72e46",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$$\\begin{align*}\\ensuremath\nu_n^3&=(2^{n+1}+1)^3=2^{3n+3}+3.2^{2n+2}+3.2^{n+1}+1=2^{3n+3}+(2+1).2^{2n+2}+(2+1).2^{n+1}+1\\\\\n &=2^{3n+3}+2^{2n+3}+2^{2n+2}+2^{n+2}+2^{n+1}+1=10...0110...0110...01_2\n\\end{align*}$$\n\n($n-1$ puis $n-1$ puis $n$ chiffres $0$)",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\\ensuremath\nu_n^3&amp;=(2^{n+1}+1)^3=2^{3n+3}+3.2^{2n+2}+3.2^{n+1}+1=2^{3n+3}+(2+1).2^{2n+2}+(2+1).2^{n+1}+1\\\\\n&amp;=2^{3n+3}+2^{2n+3}+2^{2n+2}+2^{n+2}+2^{n+1}+1=10...0110...0110...01_2\n\\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n<p>(<span class=\"math inline\">\\(n-1\\)</span> puis <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(n-1\\)</span> puis <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span> chiffres <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(0\\)</span>)</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
