        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\\ensuremath\nu_n^3-u_n^2+u_n&amp;=2^{3n+3}+3.2^{2n+2}+3.2^{n+1}+1-2^{2n+2}-2^{n+2}-1+2^{n+1}+1=2^{3n+3}+2^{2n+3}+2^{n+2}+1\\\\\n&amp;=10...010...010...01\n\\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n<p>(<span class=\"math inline\">\\(n-1\\)</span> puis <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span> puis <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(n+1\\)</span> chiffres <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(0\\)</span>)</p>\n"
